  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diamond Thief is an arcade 2d platforme game.This game is a kind of Manic miner released in the 80s on Zx Spectrum and Amstrad cpc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is very simple to play, collect the diamonds in the level  and go to the exit door. More than 60 levels await you. The game allows you to continue after losing all your lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Over 60 Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Continue Support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Retro Graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Update Free</p>",
